parameters.name: AddEntry
parameters.description: The entries to be added to the prefix list.

parameters.name: Description
parameters.description: The description of the prefix list. The description must be 2 to 256 characters in length and cannot start with `http://` or `https://`.

parameters.name: PrefixListId
parameters.description: The ID of the prefix list.

parameters.name: PrefixListName
parameters.description: The name of the prefix list. The name must be 2 to 128 characters in length. It must start with a letter and cannot start with `http://`, `https://`, `com.aliyun`, or `com.alibabacloud`. The name can contain letters, digits, colons (:), underscores (\_), periods (.), and hyphens (-).

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The region ID of the prefix list. You can call the [DescribeRegions](~~25609~~) operation to query the most recent region list.

parameters.name: RemoveEntry
parameters.description: The entries to be deleted from the prefix list.
